text: Kim Soo-nyung (born April 5, 1971) is a retired South Korean archer. Kim competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, 1992 Summer Olympics, and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Kim Su-NyeongSoo-Nyung KIM ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic silver medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic bronze medalists for South Korea
